<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> kOyil kulacEkaratEvaṟku yāṇṭu 2 vaikāci mātam 1 ti kīḷ kOṉāṭṭuk
<lb n="2"/>kūḻaikuḷattūr <unclear>Ū</unclear>rāka Icainta Ūravarōm Ivvūr nāyiṉār cu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ntiracōḷi<hi rend="grantha">sva</hi>ram Uṭaiya nāyaṉārkku tirunāmattukkāṇiyāka nilavilai
<lb n="4"/><hi rend="grantha">pramā</hi>ṇam paṇṇikkuṭutta paricāvatu Iṟṟaināḷ peruṅkaḷūr miḻiccārāṉa
<lb n="5"/>piḷḷaipallavarāyar Iṉṉāyaṉārkku pallavaṉ cantiyāka Oṉṟu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kku Oru cantināṉāḻi ney <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> vēṇum meṉṟu Eṅkaḷ
<lb n="7"/>pakkalilē nūṟṟorupa <gap reason="lost" quantity="12" unit="character"/> catturukāla vayakkalum vaṭakkil
<lb n="8"/><unclear>pa</unclear>ṟikālum koṇṭu viṭukaiyil Iṉṉilaṅkoṇṭu nāḷ O
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṉṟukku Orucanti nāṉāḻi <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> cantirātittavarai <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/>ḷakaṭavarākavum Ippaṭi cammatittu Iṟaiyil kaḻittu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/>tiruṉāmattukkāṇi ceytu kuṭuttōm Uṭaiyār tiru <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="12"/>ya nāyaṉāṟku I <gap reason="lost" quantity="12" unit="character"/> rāka Icainta Ūravarōm <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
</p>

